subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Marion Bartoli of France, the No. 15 seed, and Sabine Lisicki of Germany, the No. 23 seed, will face each other on Saturday, and one will win their first Grand Slam title.
